<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I am currently doing the quest myself...I sudjest to any non-human doin the quest to prepare yourself for a long quest. This for me is the most difficult for non humans because humans get an advantage of obtaining the high warmly faction easier. Just a warning to all non humans, I am close, but not close enough to recieve the shield yet. BTW I am a lvl 30 cleric doing a lvl 50 quest. Yes thats why its so difficult people because it is made for level 50's. I know some level 50's that have a hard time with Grimrot because he hits hard and also has major resist! But clerics have the most touble than those paladins. Still a level 50 paly needed acouple heals, but he did need his LHs' if I wasnt there. Anyway just bracer yourself for along quest. I would also like to know of there are any Dwarfs that have completed this quest?</font></td></tr></table>
