<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Look for Lashun Novashine in north Qeynos. He will wonder from teh newbie area and the Temple of Life. Give him 2gp and or 2 bone chips. You can only give him up to 2gp at a time but you can give up to 8 bone chips at a time because of the 4 item slots. Give him about 400 bone chips and 600pp in gold and you should have your faction you need.</font></td></tr></table>
